    <description>Pangolin is an identity-aware VPN and proxy solution for zero-trust remote access to anything, anywhere. Built on WireGuard, it provides secure tunneled access to your self-hosted services and networks.

## Features

- Zero-trust network access (ZTNA)
- WireGuard-based VPN tunneling
- Identity-aware proxy
- Secure remote access to self-hosted services

**Please Note**: This is an automatically updated package. If you find it is out of date by more than a day or two, please contact the maintainer(s) and let them know the package is no longer updating correctly.
